rComments: Such an interesting and clear lecturer! Easy to get good grades if you go to class and take a lot of notes. Only did a few of the readings and managed an A+.

One of my best profs!! You can tell he really cares about his students sucess and his classes are very interesting. Gives great feedback in his corrections for the assignments. Would definitly take a class with him again!
Great class! Prof Forand is a sweetheart!

This prof is amazing! He's so nice, cares about the students, recommended me a book for my assignment, the class is in French and he's from Alberta but speaks very clearly with no trouble at all. He sang and played guitar in class for us! Best prof ever. I'll take any class he teaches!!!

Très bon cours, professeur Foran est très abordable et ses cours vraiment intéressant.  Bien sûr, il faut travailler un peu pour avoir des bonnes notes, mais il rend la matière enseignée facile à assimiler? Plus, this prof is hot hot hot?..
Prof Foran is friendly, respectful, well organized, passionate about history and a really snappy dresser.
